data.description: Single Opportunity to Own a Masterpiece Custom Home, known for its high quality finishes and amenities. With over 2,000 square feet of spacious elegance, there are custom details in every room...Tray ceilings, crown moulding, 20 in tile in living areas and baths, vinyl plank flooring in Bedrooms and Den, granite counters and large glass windows and sliders. The Beautiful and spacious Owner's suite has a view of the pool and yard. The Open Floor Plan is perfect for family living and entertaining. Gather around the eat-in kitchen granite counters, and enjoy a view of the pool and lush yard while looking out of the aquarium glass windows. Enjoy the pleasant year round Florida weather from the large screened lanai while you entertain family and friends or relax by the sparkling pool. Impress your guests with generous size bedrooms and walk-in closets as well as the granite counter tops and quality throughout among many other amenities this home offers such as the 2022 NEW ROOF and SOLAR PANELS, 19 SEER A/C, WELL, SEPTIC SYSTEM, 6 ft Privacy fence, impact windows, lawn irrigation system, Water Shield water softener, security system and a lush landscape in the backyard which gives this home a Paradise feeling you can't miss. Schedule your private showing today.
